  <main class="container">
    <h2>About the study</h2>
    <p>The CHERuB study (NIHR-funded) investigates childhood outcomes after perinatal brain injuries. We follow developmental, cognitive and health outcomes to improve care and support.</p>

    <section>
      <h3>Study overview (lay summary)</h3>
      <p>We recruit children who experienced perinatal brain injury and follow them with periodic assessments, questionnaires and routine data linkage. Our aim is to understand long-term outcomes and identify interventions.</p>
    </section>

